<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sprouts - Welcome</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="brand">Sprouts</div>
        <div>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
            <a href="#products">Products</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-buttons">
            <button onclick="location.href='/login'">Login</button>
            <button onclick="location.href='/register'">Register</button>
            <button class="cart-button" onclick="location.href='/cart'">
                <img src="/img/cart.webp" alt="Cart" class="cart-img">
            </button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to Sprouts</h1>
        <p>Your one-stop shop for all things natural and organic.</p>
        <button class="shop-now-btn" onclick="location.href='#products'">Shop Now</button>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <div class="about-content">
            <img src="/img/about.webp" alt="About Us Image" class="about-image">
            <p>Sprouts began with a simple mission: to bring the best natural and organic products to our community. Founded by a group of health enthusiasts, we believe that living a healthy lifestyle should be accessible to everyone. Our journey started in a small farmer's market, where we realized the need for a dedicated space that offers a wide range of natural and organic products. Today, Sprouts is proud to be a trusted source for quality products that support a healthy and sustainable lifestyle.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="products">
        <h2>Our Products</h2>
        <div class="product-grid">
            <div class="product-item">
                <img src="/img/productEx.webp" alt="Product 1">
                <h3>Organic Honey</h3>
                <p>$10.99</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
            <div class="product-item">
                <img src="/img/productEx.webp" alt="Product 2">
                <h3>Natural Almonds</h3>
                <p>$8.99</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
            <div class="product-item">
                <img src="/img/productEx.webp" alt="Product 3">
                <h3>Herbal Tea</h3>
                <p>$12.99</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have questions? Get in touch with us!</p>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
